snippet.title: BoneCraft Trailer for Steam Release
snippet.description:
Pack your staffs and set your Tasers to stun, BoneCraft is set to be released on Steam. Captain Fort Worth and his rowdy crew of Space Wranglers and robots will plunge their ship into the Orc and Elf-filled fantasy land of BoneCraft on Steam June 3rd, 2019.

Using the Captain's skills of seduction and his team's expertise in interstellar extinction, you will search the hostile environment of the planet for the galaxy's Holy Grail: the Elf Queen and her band of lustful minions. See more of BoneCraft on Steam at: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1001220
